      <title>AMC 将重组债务负担，利用影院支持交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/amc-to-restructure-debt-load-using-theaters-to-support-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，AMC 娱乐控股公司已与债权人达成协议，要求重组债务并将美国影院转移到该公司的其他部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/amc-to-restructure-debt-load-using-theaters-to-support-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 17:37:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杠杆金融市场通过大量交易摆脱夏季低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/leveraged-finance-markets-buck-summer-lull-with-spate-of-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于收购融资增加，借款人趁市场保持弹性、融资成本低廉之际追求重新定价等机会性交易，杠杆贷款发放量正在创下夏季新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/leveraged-finance-markets-buck-summer-lull-with-spate-of-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 17:34:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
