      <title>Clearlake 支持的盲注制造商看到竞争对手债权人囤积债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/clearlake-backed-blind-maker-sees-rival-creditors-stockpile-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街各家公司正竞相收回威斯康星州一家鲜为人知的窗帘生产商的债务，为可能引发重组战的发生做准备，而这场战事可能使它们相互竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/clearlake-backed-blind-maker-sees-rival-creditors-stockpile-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债务期限迫在眉睫，TDR 面临失去邮轮运营商 Hurtigruten 控制权的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/tdr-risks-losing-control-of-hurtigruten-as-debt-deadline-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，如果挪威邮轮运营商 Hurtigruten Group AS 未能在 8 月底之前为其明年到期的债券进行再融资，TDR Capital LLP 可能会失去对该公司控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/tdr-risks-losing-control-of-hurtigruten-as-debt-deadline-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:44:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
